## Tips
* Be careful who you send it to
* Expect that only 10% at most of your emails get a response
* Number of responses should be 15-30 to be meaningful
* Long surveys do not get answered
* Try to make it quantitative.
* Essay answers are useful but not quantitative
* Don't flood university community with surveys, especially non-students

